<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Privacy Policy</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-gray-100 text-gray-800">
  <header class="bg-red-500 text-white p-6 shadow-md">
    <h1 class="text-center text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
  </header>
  <main class="container mx-auto p-6 bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg mt-6">
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Introduction</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our services.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and payment details when you use our platform.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        We use your information to provide and improve our services, process transactions, and communicate with you.
      </p>
    </section>
    <section class="mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. Please contact us if you have any concerns.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
  <footer class="bg-red-500 text-white p-4 text-center mt-6">
    <p>&copy; 2025 Airbnb Clone. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>